Design a Lucky 7 game using PHP and HTML. The rules are as follows -


min 1 end mix 6

1 round  1 2 =3

The game contains 2 dice

The user starts with 100 Rs
At the start of every round, User bets 10 Rs.

The user has three options to choose from - below 7, lucky 7 and above 7

Dice are rolled and their sums are calculated

If the user bet and dice rolled sum match, user wins 20 Rs. If its lucky 7 that user bet and sum is 7 user wins 30 Rs
else user looses